<div class="wrapper row3">
    <main class="hoc container clear">
        <div class="content">
            <h1 id="title" style="font-size: 40px">We're Anything But Imaginary...</h1>
            <img class="imgr borderedbox inspace-5" src="~/Content/Images/84875.jpg" style="width:auto; height:auto; max-height:150px; max-width:150px" />
            <p>When asked about the Imaginary Cage, the same questions always arise.  How does a place like this exist?  Are there really people out there with mythical creatures for pets? Do we live in Harry Potter's universe? Unfortunately, we can't say yes to all of those questions, but we want to bring a sanctuary to beasts of all mystical, mythical, fantastical, and just outright unknown to common eyes. </p>

            <p>We use magic to bring forth portals to safely transport your wondrous friends to beautiful havens where they can run, feed, and be themselves outside of the public eye.  We have made it easy for anyone in the area to come to one of our <a href="~/Views/ResortLocations/Index.cshtml">Resort Locations</a>to check us out.  We make sure to bring safe, affordable, and accessible support when it comes to you and your magical friend.</p>
            <hr />
            <img class="imgl borderedbox inspace-5" src="~/Content/Images/kundan-ramisetti-146.jpg" style= "width: auto; height: auto; max-width: 150px; max-height: 150px" />
            <p>Imaginary Cage first started in 1992 when more and more sightings of creatures were popping up.  From the Loch Ness Monster to Bigfoot, people were out searching for these amazing beings and those who housed these animals were having a harder time trying to keep them safe when they couldn't watch them.</p>

            <p>We started this resort not only as a means to keep these unique animals safe and their owners worry-free, but also for those who doubt their existence can have the chance to believe.  In a world where the magic is fading in favor of technology or money, we want to bring imagination to reality in hopes that the magic return.  For those who have an animal different from this world, we invite you to resorts in hopes that you will consider us for your animal's supervision.  For those without one of these creatures, we encourage you to keep the magic alive and find time to learn and understand them.  Thank you for joining us today and keep on believing!</p>
        </div>
    </main>
</div>

